Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,人好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,請問你們在找什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看 這件絕對合身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,還有其他的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,野中 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,澪？
